@0 = ~The local cemetery is haunted by the undead at night. Bring weapons to visit Grandma or don't visit her at all. It all started after some sorcerer from the Luskan's Arcane Brotherhood was buried there.~/*En el cartel pone: "¡CUIDADO! Los muertos vivientes están alborotados. Si quieres visitar a la abuela, trae armas o no la visites. En serio". Firmado: El vigilante.*/
@1 = ~In Luskan, the High Captains are at war with each other. That's why they closed the gates.~/*"¿Y por qué su diosa quiere que se peleen entre sí?" Eso es lo que dicen todos. Cómo lo odio.*/
@2 = ~South of the Green Gryphon, the road to Port Llast became dangerous. After Luskan stopped patrolling the road, travelers began to be attacked by creatures like orcs and bugbears. They used to sit quietly in their caves, but they say someone controls them.~/*Fallaste a los muchachos de Puerto Final. Prepárate a morir. Este guerrero parece preparado para enfrentarse a toda una horda de orcos y trasgos. Hay reyes y tiranos, pero yo no sirvo a ninguno de ellos.*/
@3 = ~They say there are werewolves in Port Llast, attacking the locals at night and tearing them apart. Now they've gotten here, people saw a werewolf near the tavern the other day.~/*Dicen que hay algo que celebrar; que los muertos han vuelto a su polvoriento sueño, por así decirlo. Bien por ti si salvaste la situación.*/
@4 = ~There's a nasty cult in the area. They say Lady Aribeth herself is here to catch them.~/*¿Hay alguna arboleda druídica en la zona? ¿Cómo se ha enfrentado Lady Aribeth a la plaga?*/
@5 = ~Five dangerous criminals have escaped from Waterdeep's prison. It's doubtful, but still possible, that they went straight here. There's a minotaur who's taken up residence here, locked himself in his room and won't come out, only demanding food and ale. So I wondered if he's a criminal, he looks like a bandit.~/*"¿Qué te hace pensar que he escapado de algún lugar?" Tengo aquí una de las gemas. En este amuleto aparece el retrato de un gólem a un lado y una runa de custodia en el otro. Supongo que conoces el aspecto que tiene un demonio.*/
@6 = ~There's been no word from Charwood for a long time. Rumor has it there's a lot of undead, ghosts, it's creepy.~/*No hay nada que puedas hacer aquí en este momento. "¿Has dicho que hay muertos vivientes ahí afuera?"*/
@7 = ~Neverwinter Wood is best not to go there. They say the animals there have gone wild, even the deer and rabbits are attacking everyone.~
/*Bosques de Noyvern: corazón del bosque El sol reluce sobre el cuadrante, la sombra señala la hora.*/